<paragraph blockId="13.[211,1171,1180,1275]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1269">
The specific name “mery” is in honour of my sister 
<taxonomicName authority="Asenjo" authorityName="Asenjo &amp; Ribeiro-Costa" authorityYear="2013" box="[810,963,1219,1244]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Leptochirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="1268" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mery">Mery Asenjo</taxonomicName>
